title: Can't miss this beautiful 2 bed 2 bath garden apartment
posting_body: ['Here at The Edge at NoDa we offer lovely 1 & 2 bedroom garden apartments as well as 2 bedroom townhomes.', "With these great options we're confident you'll find your next home here with us.", "The listing price includes valet trash, renter's insurance, washer/dryer, pest control and community fees.", 'Featuring a salt water pool and a great gym for your daily workouts.', 'Located at "the edge of NoDa" puts us just a short drive to all areas of detroit metro.', 'Conveniently located near uptown, university and plaza midwood.', 'What are you waiting for?', "We're ready to welcome you home!!!", 'Pricing is subject to change, call for availability']
